    <h2>1. Delhi-NCR: India's Largest Bakery Equipment Manufacturing Hub</h2>
    <p>Delhi-NCR is the single largest cluster for commercial bakery and food equipment manufacturing in India. The concentration of factories in industrial areas like Naraina, Okhla Phase I–III, Wazirpur, and the satellite cities of Faridabad and Noida means you can visit multiple manufacturers in a single day.</p>

    <h3>What Delhi Manufacturers Make</h3>
    <p>Delhi-NCR manufacturers cover the full spectrum: convection ovens, deck ovens, bread slicers, dough proofers, display refrigerators, hot display cases, display counters, bakery trolleys, and custom stainless steel fabrications. Many Delhi factories are OEM suppliers to well-known brands — meaning the same physical product may be sold under different brand names at very different prices.</p>

    <h3>Key Delhi-NCR Manufacturers</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Genius Baking Equipment (Naraina, Delhi):</strong> One of India's most established bakery oven manufacturers. Produces convection ovens, deck ovens, proofers, and rotary rack ovens under their own brand and for OEM clients. Factory visits are welcome by appointment. Ex-factory pricing for a 10-tray convection oven starts around ₹1.1 lakh.</li>
      <li><strong>Ekon India (Okhla Industrial Area, Delhi):</strong> Specialises in commercial refrigeration and display equipment for bakeries. Strong presence across India with a good dealer network. Factory-direct pricing available for bulk orders of 5+ units.</li>
      <li><strong>Prism Bake (Faridabad, Haryana):</strong> Mid-size manufacturer of deck ovens and convection ovens. Known for solid build quality at competitive prices. MOQ of 1 unit for standard models. Good customization options for deck sizes and heating configurations.</li>
      <li><strong>Vijay Kitchen Equipment (Wazirpur, Delhi):</strong> Fabricator of stainless steel bakery furniture, display cases, bread racks, and prep tables. Custom work is their strength — they'll build exactly to your measurements. Lead time 10–20 days for custom orders.</li>
      <li><strong>India Bakery Equipment (Noida, UP):</strong> Newer manufacturer with a focus on value-segment ovens and mixers. Competitive on price; growing dealer network. Ideal for bakeries on a tight budget that need reliable basic equipment.</li>
    </ul>

