    <h3>How to Approach Delhi Manufacturers</h3>
    <p>The best way to approach Delhi-NCR manufacturers is to call or WhatsApp ahead with your specific requirement (equipment type, capacity, electric/gas, daily production volume) and ask to schedule a factory visit. Most factories in Naraina and Okhla are accessible by metro (Green Line to Inderlok or Naraina Vihar stations). Bring your specifications in writing. Negotiate payment terms: most manufacturers offer 50% advance, 50% before dispatch. For repeat orders, credit terms of 30–45 days are possible.</p>

