    <h2>9. Warranty Terms: What to Expect from Indian Manufacturers</h2>
    <p>Warranty terms vary widely and are often negotiable, especially on large orders. Understanding the typical range helps you ask the right questions.</p>

    <h3>Standard Warranty Coverage in India (2026)</h3>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Manufacturer Tier</th><th>Parts Warranty</th><th>Labour Warranty</th><th>Typical Exclusions</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Budget Indian manufacturer</td><td>6 months</td><td>3 months</td><td>Heating elements, seals, normal wear</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Mid-range Indian manufacturer</td><td>12 months</td><td>6 months</td><td>Heating elements after 6 months, consumables</td></tr>
